casebody.data:
Ronald Tyler v. Lawrence Tilghman, Warden (9454)

Norcott, Cretella and Heiman, Js.

Argued May 31 decision released June 25, 1991 Edan F. Calabrese, for the appellant (petitioner). Marjorie Allen Dauster, deputy assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Walter D. Flanagan, state’s attorney, and Christopher Alexy, deputy assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (respondent). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
